From: Rodrigo Gobbi <rodrigo.gobbi.7@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:47:38 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] staging: rtl8723bs: remove unused debug statements
Git-commit: ea5e911e14cebfc9832728c27f05e43b086fec0c
Patch-mainline: v6.13-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Remove both commented printk() and commented DEBUG_ERR()
statements around the driver.

Signed-off-by: Rodrigo Gobbi <rodrigo.gobbi.7@gmail.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20241015014738.41685-3-rodrigo.gobbi.7@gmail.com
Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
